<br>
That incident with the Broodmother I mentioned <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> did</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> happen. For the record, this is a notoriously buggy quest, and I did a lot of reading up about it before I attempted. I had a group to kill Fergul, saw on track that she was up, ran invis through the caves to reach her, turned in the harness, and recieved the quest message. She started moving, and I informed the zone that I was triggering the Broodmother and to stay clear of the giant fort for their own safety. Everything went fine until the Broodmother reached the gates...and promptly turned to the side and walked off. The two named giants did not spawn, she did not attack, nothing. <br>
<br>
